<br />\n<br />\n雖然2019年整體樓價升幅不足2%，但本報統計35個鐵路沿線私人屋苑，仍有25個屋苑錄得升幅，比例逾七成，當中七個屋苑升幅達雙位數。其中青衣盈翠半島平均呎價升至18,486元，與2018年12月平均呎價15,521元比較，一年漲價19%，成為2019年鐵路盤「升幅王」。2018年年底，盈翠半島逆市破頂，11座高層F室海景戶以1,548萬元沽出，呎價20,052萬元成為屋苑歷來最貴分層戶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191231/large/1577793957_5116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191231%2Flarge%2F1577793957_5116.jpg&h=a3c6617f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200101/60436706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200101%2F60436706&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as1UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=472b563e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200101%2F60436706&h=72ab0a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200101/60436706</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"唔係好插je<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a17f7cb4b792db03d125878b8d7e022042b146c","tid":1805861,"uid":195334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"升幅收窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跌啊仆街"},{"pid":"ef86b1b8acc9321fb2ea3dae894c9cf1f2799c83","tid":1805861,"uid":19217,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a17f7cb4b792db03d125878b8d7e022042b146c","tid":1805861,"uid":195334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"升幅收窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跌啊仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"宜家唔買 遲d全部800萬上車"},{"pid":"36d5f522a99d472f21f8df4857c88fe7132cbfe8","tid":1805861,"uid":137569,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:03:48.